Decompress the dependencies: 
  - in the folder axe/: http://www.gbresearch.com/axe/ (tested only with 1.5.4.164)
  - in the folder pugixml/: http://pugixml.org/ (tested only with 1.7)
  
Required compilers: support C++11. 
Complete project successfully tested with GCC 4.9.2, Visual Studio 2013, Visual Studio 2015 Update 2 (not previous versions of 2015); others not tried. 